                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5432" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0172</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8544 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">何去何从：数知科技的巨额商誉减值风波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Where to go: Shuzhi Technology&#39;s huge impairment of goodwill</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李春玲，刘佩佩，陈紫荆，陈嘉奕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京数知科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数知科技；溢价并购；企业估值；商誉减值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shuzhi Technology; premium mergers and acquisitions; business valuation;impairment of goodwill </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017年北京数知科技股份有限公司以63亿元人民币的对价并购了Blackbird Hypersonic Investments Ltd（以下简称BBHI），形成了约56亿元商誉。2020年12月一纸公告让数知科技跌到了谷底深渊，陷入舆论漩涡。公告显示，数知科技公司控股的多家子公司业绩出现滑坡，经营状况显现恶化迹象，同时公告披露该公司存在巨额的商誉减值风险，预计计提减值的金额高达61亿。更加令人吃惊的是，其旗下的子公司中商誉减值占比最大的是BBHI！要知道，BBHI此前三年在商界备受瞩目，三年前数知科技高溢价将其纳入麾下，BBHI也不负众望，三年内业绩稳步抬升并完成了并购时的业绩承诺。此次公告揭露的“迷之商誉”的问题立即被交易所问询并发了关注函。本案例以数知科技商誉巨额减值“暴雷”为切入点，着重分析了其因战略转型并购BBHI公司的前因后果以及后续商誉减值为公司带来的不良影响，旨在引导学生关注企业的并购的动因以及溢价并购带来的商誉减值风险，并探寻企业如何防止商誉恶化的巨大风险。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2017, Beijing Shuzhi Technology Co., Ltd. acquired Blackbird Hypersonic Investments Ltd (hereinafter referred to as BBHI) for a consideration of RMB 6.3 billion, and formed a goodwill of approximately RMB 5.6 billion. A paper announcement in December 2020 brought Shuzhi Technology to the bottom of the abyss and plunged into a whirlpool of public opinion. The announcement shows that the performance of many subsidiaries controlled by Shuzhi Technology has declined and the operating conditions are showing signs of deterioration. At the same time, the announcement discloses that the company has a huge risk of impairment of goodwill, and the estimated amount of impairment is as high as 6.1 billion. What is even more surprising is that BBHI has the largest percentage of goodwill impairment among its subsidiaries! You know, BBHI has attracted much attention in the business world in the previous three years. Three years ago, Shuzhi Technology included it at a high premium. BBHI has also lived up to expectations. The performance of the first three years has been improved steadily, and the performance commitment during the merger and acquisition period.The issue of &quot;Mystery of Goodwill&quot; revealed in this announcement was immediately inquired by the exchange and issued a letter of concern. This case uses the &quot;Thunderstorm&quot; of Shuzhi Technology’s huge impairment of goodwill as an entry point, and focuses on the analysis of the causes and consequences of the merger and acquisition of BBHI due to strategic transformation and the adverse effects of subsequent impairment of goodwill to the company. Our purpose is to guide students to pay attention to the motivations of corporate mergers and acquisitions, as well as the risk of goodwill impairment caused by premium mergers and acquisitions, and to think about how Chinese enterprises should prevent the risk of goodwill impairment. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《公司并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业价值评估 商誉产生原因</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-07</td>
                            </tr>
